# `parsomics-metapackage`

A metapackage for the parsomics project. It includes:

- parsomics-cli
- parsomics-core
- parsomics-api-server
- parsomics-plugin-clean
- parsomics-plugin-dbcan
- parsomics-plugin-interpro
- parsomics-plugin-proteinfer
